      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior has some noticeable wear on the upholstery from regular use. However, the engine starts reliably and the car has been maintained to ensure it remains safe and roadworthy. It is a solid, practical choice for someone prioritizing utility and reliability over cosmetic perfection.",
